<Author>xplosiv
<Content>Near the airport I stayed alone in this hotel last August. Before flying out I did the usual of looking up hotels and reading the reviews but it's always difficult to make a decision! As I travel alone regularly I tend to go to hotels where there are fewer rooms as it makes me feel safer.This hotel is near the airport and I can see that it would definately suit business people as opposed to young travellers as it is probably too quiet. However the train station is only a 10 minute walk away.The room was clean and the staff were friendly....other than that the hotel was ok.There is an Italian restaurant attached to this hotel where the food was ok and the sevice was good. I tended to eat out in Berlin and come back and sit on the terrace to enjoy a few beers.This is a good hotel to stay in if you don't want to be in the hustle and bustle of the city or if you want to be close to the airport. 
